column2: OK INTO THE BLACKHAWK, LETS GO! LETS GO!
EVERYBODY IS ONBOARD. GO GO GO!
WELL DONE PEOPLE. GOOD MISSION AND FUN TOO. HOOAYH!
ENTERING INTO ENEMY TERRITORY. GET READY PEOPLE.
LEAVING ENEMY TERRITORY. OK GUYS, YOU CAN START BREATHING AGAIN. EXCELLENT JOB, I'M PROUD OF ALL OF YOU.
PAPABEAR TO ALL FORCES IN THE REGION. I'M GLAD TO ANNOUNCE THAT OUR RESCUE ATTEMPT WAS BEEN SUCCESFUL. OUR FORCES HAVE NOW ENTERED TO FRIENDLY TERRITORY SAFELY. PAPABEAR OUT.
